pullrequest.title: Clean up internal resources when a model gets removed

content.raw: When resolving the conflict in the Changlog, I saw that 1.5.0 is listed as released. But we only have a prerelease of 1.5. Should I put the entry for this PR under 1.5? Should I remove the date from the 1.5.0 entry since it's not released yet?
